div(class='modal upload-photo', id='uploadPhoto')
    div(class='modal__layer upload-photo__layer', data-micromodal-close)
        .modal__inner 
            form(class='modal__body upload-photo__content')
                div(class='modal__body_head upload-photo__content_head')
                    h2(class='modal__body_head_title upload-photo__content_head_title')  Загрузить новое фото
                    button(class='modal__body_head_close', type='button', data-micromodal-close)
                        img(src="./img/icons/close-gray.svg", alt="")
                .upload-photo__content_img 
                    div(class='upload-photo__content_img_in', )
                        .upload-photo__content_img_text Нажмите для загрузки фото или перетащите файл в область 
                        div(class='upload-photo__content_img_text_in' id='upload-photo', data-method='POST', data-url='./files')
                    .upload-photo__content_img_action   
                        button(class='upload-photo__content_img_action_change button button-aqua', type='button')
                            .text Загрузить другое фото
                        button(class='upload-photo__content_img_action_remove button button-aqua button-func', type='button')
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
